article_title: Suicide Bombing in Pakistan Kills Nine
article_text:
PESHAWAR, Pakistan—A suicide bomb ripped through a restaurant in the volatile northwestern city of Peshawar on Tuesday, killing at least nine, officials said, just as the government and Islamist militants prepared to meet for peace talks.

The attack was apparently aimed at members of the Shiite Muslim minority. A man wearing a suicide vest...
